## Run staging stack locally

```powershell
npm run test:staging
```

Uses `.env.staging`, migrates **`pBookspro_Staging`**, API on port **3001**, staging Electron client.

**Watch mode:** `npm run test:staging:watch`

**API only:**

```powershell
npm run start:backend:staging    # compiled API, port 3001
npm run dev:backend:staging      # tsx watch, port 3001
```

**Production API only:**

```powershell
npm run start:backend:production   # port 3000
npm run dev:backend:production
```

